file_content.text: Well done, hunter.
Looks like you made it, hunter. I'll admit, I am quite impressed.
Have we met?
You look familiar.
Of course, who wouldn't be?
Obviously.
No one I can think of.
I'm not signing autographs.
Don't bother me.
I just wanted to offer my congratulations.
Name's Q'kal. I was one of the hunters in your group on Dromund Kaas, the one who dropped out. I regret that decision now.
Everyone has to know their limitations.
You shouldn't.
I won't argue with that.
There's always the next Great Hunt.
You'll get another shot.
Yeah, next time, I won't leave.
Smartest thing you ever did, chump.
I would have killed you.
Yeah, after seeing you in action I knew I wasn't ready, but I will be next time.
You've been an inspiration to me. To quite a few hunters, actually.
It was an honor meeting you. A true honor.
